name: Planet R Fluorite
description: Planet R Fluorite is the planet of energy transformation. This planet enhances energetic protection and intuition. Here unfounded worries are cleansed and positivity flows. This planet provides clear thinking and clarity. It is here that creative inspiration flourishes due to being able to focus and see the bigger picture. This planet includes LED changing colored lights, and it glows differently under UV light, regular light, and no light.
